\section{Summary of API Additions}
%% ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

\begin{center}
\begin{longtable}{l p{8.5cm}}
\toprule
\textbf{Symbol} & \textbf{Description} \\
\midrule
\endhead
\texttt{CG\_LIBVER\_EARLIEST}   & Oldest CGNS library version (1050). \\
\texttt{CG\_LIBVER\_LATEST}     & Current library version (5000). \\
\texttt{CG\_LIBVER\_AUTO}       & Sentinel: automatic write-version selection. \\
\texttt{CG\_LIBVER\_V30}\ldots\texttt{CG\_LIBVER\_V50} & Specific version milestone constants. \\
\texttt{CG\_CONFIG\_SET\_COMPAT\_VERSION} & \texttt{cg\_configure} token: set global compatibility version. \\
\texttt{CG\_CONFIG\_GET\_COMPAT\_VERSION} & \texttt{cg\_configure} token: query global compatibility version. \\
\texttt{CG\_CONFIG\_WRITE\_VERSION}       & \texttt{cg\_configure} token: set write version. \\
\texttt{CG\_CONFIG\_GET\_WRITE\_VERSION}  & \texttt{cg\_configure} token: query write version. \\
\texttt{CG\_PARAM\_KEY}         & Enum of parameter keys (100--103). \\
\texttt{cg\_parameters\_t}      & Opaque parameter object type. \\
\texttt{CG\_PARAMS\_DEFAULT}    & NULL sentinel: use global configuration. \\
\texttt{cg\_set\_compat\_version}         & Set global compatibility version. \\
\texttt{cg\_set\_file\_compat\_version}   & Set per-file compatibility version. \\
\texttt{cg\_get\_file\_compat\_version}   & Query per-file compatibility version and/or minimum required version.  Any output pointer may be \texttt{NULL}; the $O(N)$ feature scan runs only when \texttt{min\_version} is non-\texttt{NULL}. \\
\texttt{cg\_params\_create}     & Allocate parameter object with defaults. \\
\texttt{cg\_params\_destroy}    & Free parameter object. \\
\texttt{cg\_params\_set}        & Set a parameter by key/value. \\
\texttt{cg\_open\_with\_params} & Open file with explicit parameter object (standard name). \\
\texttt{CGNS\_NO\_MACROS}      & Preprocessor guard: when defined, suppresses the polymorphic \texttt{cg\_open} macro so \texttt{cg\_open} resolves to the real 3-argument function. \\
\texttt{cg\_open} (macro)       & Polymorphic: 3-arg (legacy) or 4-arg (with params); suppressed by \texttt{\#define CGNS\_NO\_MACROS}. \\
\texttt{CGNSMinRequiredVersion\_t} & \emph{Alt.~B:} new SIDS node recording the minimum CGNS version required to read the file.  Preserves \texttt{CGNSLibraryVersion\_t} semantics. \\
\texttt{\_CGNS\_FeatureMask}   & Hidden \texttt{uint64\_t} attribute (HDF5: \texttt{H5T\_NATIVE\_UINT64}; ADF: \texttt{U8}): bitmask of features present; enables $O(1)$ version check on open. Placed on \texttt{CGNSMinRequiredVersion\_t} (Alt.~B) or \texttt{CGNSLibraryVersion\_t} (Alt.~A). \\
\texttt{cg\_set\_compat\_version\_f}      & Fortran: global compatibility version. \\
\texttt{cg\_set\_file\_compat\_version\_f} & Fortran: per-file compatibility version. \\
\texttt{cg\_get\_file\_compat\_version\_f} & Fortran: query per-file compatibility version and/or minimum required version. \\
\texttt{cg\_open\_params\_f}    & Fortran: 4-argument open with params. \\
\texttt{cgp\_open\_params\_f}   & Fortran (parallel): 4-argument open with params. \\
\bottomrule
\end{longtable}
\end{center}

